Package: FactorForecasting
Type: Package
Title: Factor-Based Forecasting with PCA and PLS
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sebastian", "Alamo Alonso", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A modular framework for factor-based forecasting using PCA and PLS.
    Implements direct forecast models (DI, DIAR, DIAR-LAG) with rolling and recursive
    estimation windows. Based on Bae (2024) methodology for macroeconomic forecasting.
